al/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要再上去睇下先,好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72ff491d8cb52144fb0e176862247871d7e8bb5","tid":2321934,"uid":82752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<br />\n你個棟樓爆撚硬武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e8fc51b522906058d926dddf2b33230b91b4d1","tid":2321934,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"一定要通知管理處，佢會叫樓上維修，自己唔洗勞氣"},{"pid":"3411500bbe3279e38109ec9b63833e8807a50581","tid":2321934,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"bfaa87e21893c169acea5916f6f7008202439fc0","tid":2321934,"uid":359522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"72bfc77f821118e4849beaad472b76a5003bc821","tid":2321934,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"條喉不在樓上範圍，維修費誰負責？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"使用係樓上用，樓上負責"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:13:39.000Z","msg":"因為在下層範圍，如果下層唔小心整爛冇理由上層負責。 實拗數"},{"pid":"7811d49cef0786b4ea77a5bc3005d431032c5590","tid":2321934,"uid":359522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3411500bbe3279e38109ec9b63833e8807a50581","tid":2321934,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"bfaa87e21893c169acea5916f6f7008202439fc0","tid":2321934,"uid":359522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"72bfc77f821118e4849beaad472b76a5003bc821","tid":2321934,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"條喉不在樓上範圍，維修費誰負責？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"使用係樓上用，樓上負責"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:13:39.000Z","msg":"因為在下層範圍，如果下層唔小心整爛冇理由上層負責。 實拗數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b885a5462739a75fe79b8cfa1953cd7b2